House Rules Series 3 Episode 38

It's judgement day on with our final three teams fighting for a place in the grand final. With time running out, the remaining teams are crashing through the chaos to the finish line. Seven days ago, our teams were given a unique challenge. And now it's up to judges Joe Snell and Wendy Moore to deliver the most important verdict of the competition so far. Their combined scores will determine which two teams will win a coveted place in the grandfinal
